  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.6">
<l>kāṟṟiṭaip pūḷai karantaṉa varantai yuṟakkaṭa larakkartañ cēṉai</l>
<l>kūṟṟiṭaic cellak koṭuṅkaṇai turanta kōlavi lirāmaṉṟaṉ kōyil</l>
<l>ūṟṟiṭai niṉṟa vāḻaiyiṉ kaṉika ḷūḻttuvīḻn taṉavuṇṭu maṇṭi</l>
<l>cēṟṟiṭaik kayalka ḷukaḷtikaḻ vayalcūḻ tiruveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple of Rāma with a shapely bow which discharged cruel arrows</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the demon army, [like] an ocean, went into the midst of Hell,</l>
<l>So [they] felt the [same] anguish [as] silk cotton [petals] obliterated</l>
<l rend="indent">in the midst of a gale,</l>
<l>Is that very one - Tiruveḷḷiyaṅkuṭi encircled by shimmering paddy fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where kayal [fish] leap in the midst of a mire,</l>
<l>Snatching and eating fruit which had fallen, having ripened on banana [trees]</l>
<l rend="indent">which stand in the midst of a spring.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
